ription":"The Royal Exchange was organized in January 1571 by Sir Thomas Gresham. Gresham is known as the father of English banking.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When Anne Harwyne was born in 1550, in Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, England, her father, Roger Harwyne, was 20 and her mother, Catherie Ann Bury, was 26. She married John Fuller II on 15 September 1571, in Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 2 sons. She died in April 1573, in her hometown, at the age of 23, and was buried in Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, England."},"et":{"1550–April 1573":"1550–aprill 1573","1550–1573":"1550–1573","1553–1599":"1553–1599","1534–1599":"1534–1599","1572–Male":"1572–Surnud","1572–1638":"1572–1638","1530–1580":"1530–1580","1525–Female":"1525–Surnud","15 Sep 1571":"15. september 1571","1550":"1550","1572":"1572","1571":"1571","1580":"1580","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1525":"1525","1534":"1534","1599":"1599","19 October 1572":"19. oktoober 1572","April 1573":"aprill 1573","1553":"1553","1530":"1530","1573":"1573","23 April 1573":"23. aprill 1573","1638":"1638","Topcroft, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Topcroft, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Redenhall, Norfolk, England":"Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, England":"Redenhall with Harleston, Norfolk, England"},"fi":{"1550–April 1573":"1550–huhtikuu 1573","1550–1573":"1550–1573","1553–1599":"1553–1599","1534–1599":"1534–1599","1572–Male":"1572–Kuollut","1572–1638":"1572–1638","1530–1580":"1530–1580","1525–Female":"1525–Kuollut","15 Sep 1571":"15. syyskuuta 1571","1550":"1550","1572":"1572","1571":"1571","1580":"1580","1569":"1569","1558":"1558","1525":"1525","1534":"1534","1599":"1599","19 October 1572":"19. lokakuuta 1572","April 1573":"huhtikuu 1573","1553":"1553","1530":"1530","1573":"1573","23 April 1573":"23. huhtikuuta 1573","1638":"1638","Topcroft, Norfolk, England, United K